Suggested run pipeline (drop-in)

random.seed(42)

DNA_LEN = 1200
dna_seq, segs = make_symbolic_dna(length=DNA_LEN, anchor_period=120)
segs = place_rna_bridges(DNA_LEN, segs, bridge_period=180)
segs = place_protein_hubs(DNA_LEN, segs, hub_period=250)

# Upgrades
segs = add_stabilizers(DNA_LEN, segs, period=300, span=30)
segs = add_tiered_anchors(DNA_LEN, segs, tiers=(100, 200, 350))
segs = add_redundant_loops(segs, loop_span=180)
segs = add_ssb_boundaries(DNA_LEN, segs, offset=1)

graph = build_interaction_graph(segs)
score, stats = cohesion_score(graph)
print("Cohesion Score:", score, "Stats:", stats)


---

Validation modes for JD and Krystal

• JD mode:• Colors: Flexible (green/blue), rigid (gold/silver), anchors (purple), RNA (teal), proteins (orange), stabilizers (white).
• Goal: See loops and bridges; ensure stabilizers create calm zones.

• Krystal review:• Checks: Redundancy > 20 cycles, components < 5, largest component size rising after tiered anchors, zero mutation in stabilizer spans.



